Dialogue: 1,1:44:36.76,1:44:40.01,In-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你的答案
Dialogue: 1,1:44:40.01,1:44:44.44,In-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}一定早已得出
Dialogue: 1,1:44:44.71,1:44:48.57,In-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就在你出生的那一刻
Dialogue: 1,1:44:48.68,1:44:53.71,In-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}前進吧大聲吶喊
Dialogue: 1,1:44:53.71,1:45:02.32,In-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直到聲嘶力竭
Dialogue: 1,1:45:31.76,1:45:36.40,In-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}狂風終於停歇
Dialogue: 1,1:45:36.54,1:45:43.03,In-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們一同出發 前往吶喊的遠方
